refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public arraySoapClient::__getFunctions




 Returns an array of functions described in the WSDL for the Web service.

&soap.wsdl.mode.only;

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 The array of SOAP function prototypes, detailing the return type,
 the function name and type-hinted paramaters.

&reftitle.examples;
SoapClient::__getFunctions example
<?php $client = new SoapClient('http://soap.amazon.com/schemas3/AmazonWebServices.wsdl'); var_dump($client->__getFunctions()); ?>
&example.outputs;
